02:27.625 --> 02:29.540
[laughter]

02:29.584 --> 02:30.541
- There you are.

02:30.585 --> 02:32.195
I knew you'd get lost.

02:32.239 --> 02:34.589
All the new medical directors
get lost.

02:51.606 --> 02:53.390
I'll take those odds.

02:53.434 --> 02:56.393
[funky music]

02:56.437 --> 03:01.485
