♪

41:10.816 --> 41:12.339
- Because of you.

41:12.382 --> 41:14.123
♪

41:14.167 --> 41:16.604
People are excited, Max.

41:16.648 --> 41:18.301
For the first time
in a long time,

41:18.345 --> 41:20.478
they are excited
to be doctors again.

41:20.521 --> 41:22.131
♪

41:22.175 --> 41:24.525
I wanna be excited too.

